Barry Williams (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barry_Williams_(actor) 0 Barry William Blenkhorn (born September 30, 1954), known professionally as Barry Williams, is an American actor and singer best known for his role as the eldest of the Brady sons, Greg Brady, on the ABC television series The Brady Bunch.
